metadata:
  section_id: 4
  section_name: رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
  hadith_first: 24
  hadith_last: 31

hadiths[8]{hadithnumber,text,grades,reference,international_number,narrator_chain,chapter_intro}:
24,"""The hair of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) came down to the middle of his ears.”",,,24,"Anas ibn Malik said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
25,"""I used to perform the major ritual ablution, I and Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) from a single basin, and he had hair above the shoulder level and below the earlobes.”",,,25,"'A’isha said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
26,"“Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) was of medium height, broad-shouldered, and the hair of his head touched the lobes of his ears.”",,,26,"Al-Bara’ ibn 'Azib said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
27,"“I said to Anas: ‘How was the hair of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace)?' He replied: 'It was neither crisply curled nor lank. His hair used to reach the lobes of his ears'.”",,,27,"Qatada said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
28,"""Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) arrived boldly at Mecca, and he had four braids of hair.”",,,28,"Umm Hani bint 'Ali ibn Talib said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
29,"""The hair of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) was down to the middle parts of his ears.”",,,29,"Anas said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
30,"“Allah’s Messenger(Allah bless him and give him peace) used to let his hair hang down [over his face], whereas the polytheists used to part the hair of their heads. The People of the Scripture also used to let the hair of their heads hang down, and he used favor emulating the People of the Scripture with respect to things about which nothing was commanded, but Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) then parted the hair of his head.”",,,30,"Ibn 'Abbas said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
31,"""I saw Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) with four braids of hair.”",,,31,"Umm Hani said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے مبارک بالوں کا بیان
